<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>家族で楽しむ飛騨・高山大冒険！</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2c3e50;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff6b9d, #c44569, #f8b500, #e55039);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradientShift 8s ease infinite;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        @keyframes gradientShift {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, rgba(255, 107, 157, 0.1), transparent);
            animation: sparkle 3s linear infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes sparkle {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #e55039;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .family-info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #74b9ff, #0984e3);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .family-info h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .family-members {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .family-member {
            text-align: center;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }
        
        .family-member:nth-child(2) {
            animation-delay: 0.3s;
        }
        
        .family-member:nth-child(3) {
            animation-delay: 0.6s;
        }
        
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            40% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
            60% { transform: translateY(-5px); }
        }
        
        .member-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .countdown-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b9d, #c44569);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        
        .countdown-timer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .countdown-unit {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            min-width: 80px;
        }
        
        .countdown-number {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
        }
        
        .countdown-label {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .progress-bar {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            border-radius: 15px;
            height: 25px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .progress-fill {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #27ae60, #2ecc71, #f1c40f, #e67e22);
            height: 100%;
            width: 0%;
            transition: width 0.8s ease;
            border-radius: 15px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .progress-fill::after {
            content: '🚀';
            position: absolute;
            right: -15px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        
        .progress-text {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-shadow: none;
        }
        
        .excitement-meter {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b9d, #c44569);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .excitement-bar {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            height: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .excitement-fill {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f1c40f, #e67e22, #e74c3c);
            height: 100%;
            width: 0%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            animation: excitementPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
            transition: width 1s ease;
        }
        
        @keyframes excitementPulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0.8; }
            50% { opacity: 1; }
        }
        
        .family-mission {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a8e6cf, #7fcdcd);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 3px solid #4ecdc4;
        }
        
        .mission-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .mission-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .mission-list li {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .mission-list li:hover {
            transform: translateX(10px);
        }
        
        .mission-list li::before {
            content: '🎯';
            margin-right: 15px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .fun-features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .feature-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #74b9ff, #0984e3);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        
        .feature-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: shimmer 3s linear infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes shimmer {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: block;
        }
        
        .day-section {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .day-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6b9d, #c44569, #f8b500, #e55039);
        }
        
        .day-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .day-number {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b9d, #c44569);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }
        
        .day-title {
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .day-title h2 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: #e55039;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .day-subtitle {
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 40px;
        }
        
        .timeline::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 20px;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ff6b9d, #c44569, #f8b500, #e55039);
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        
        .timeline-item {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #e9ecef);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border-left: 5px solid #ff6b9d;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .timeline-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }
        
        .timeline-item::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: -47px;
            top: 30px;
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            background: #ff6b9d;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 4px solid white;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        
        .timeline-item.completed {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4edda, #c3e6cb);
            border-left-color: #28a745;
            animation: celebration 0.6s ease;
        }
        
        .timeline-item.completed::before {
            background: #28a745;
            content: '✓';
            color: white;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        @keyframes celebration {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3cd, #ffeaa7); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }
        
        .time-badge {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e55039, #c0392b);
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        .activity-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .activity-description {
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .checklist {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .checklist li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding: 8px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .checklist li:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 107, 157, 0.1);
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }
        
        .checklist input[type="checkbox"] {
            margin-right: 15px;
            transform: scale(1.5);
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .checklist input[type="checkbox"]:checked + span {
            text-decoration: line-through;
            opacity: 0.7;
            color: #28a745;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .shopping-list, .recipe-section, .map-section {
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .shopping-list {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3cd, #ffeaa7);
            border: 2px solid #f8d347;
        }
        
        .recipe-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8d7da, #f1c2c7);
            border: 2px solid #f56565;
        }
        
        .map-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d1ecf1, #bee5eb);
            border: 2px solid #17a2b8;
        }
        
        .shopping-list h4, .recipe-section h4, .map-section h4 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .shopping-list h4 {
            color: #856404;
        }
        
        .recipe-section h4 {
            color: #721c24;
        }
        
        .map-section h4 {
            color: #0c5460;
        }
        
        .recipe-steps {
            list-style: none;
            counter-reset: step-counter;
        }
        
        .recipe-steps li {
            counter-increment: step-counter;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-left: 40px;
            position: relative;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .recipe-steps li::before {
            content: counter(step-counter);
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545, #c82333);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 25px;
            height: 25px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        
        .location-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }
        
        .location-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            border-left: 5px solid #17a2b8;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .location-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }
        
        .location-card h5 {
            color: #0c5460;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        
        .location-card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .weather-widget {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #74b9ff, #0984e3);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .weather-widget::before {
            content: '☀️🌤️⛅🌦️';
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            left: -100px;
            font-size: 2rem;
            animation: weatherMove 10s linear infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes weatherMove {
            0% { left: -100px; }
            100% { left: 100%; }
        }
        
        .photo-memories {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffeaa7, #fdcb6e);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .photo-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .photo-placeholder {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
            border: 2px dashed #e17055;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .photo-placeholder:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,1);
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }
            
            .family-members {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            
            .countdown-timer {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                gap: 10px;
            }
            
            .day-header {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            
            .day-number {
                margin-right: 0;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🏔️ 家族で楽しむ飛騨・高山大冒険！ 🎉</h1>
            
            <div class="family-info">
                <h2>🚗 家族3人の素敵な旅行 🚗</h2>
                <p>2025年9月27日（土）〜 9月28日（日）</p>
                <div class="family-members">
                    <div class="family-member">
                        <div class="member-icon">👨‍💼</div>
                        <div>パパ</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="family-member">
                        <div class="member-icon">👩‍💼</div>
                        <div>ママ</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="family-member">
                        <div class="member-icon">👨‍🎓</div>
                        <div>息子さん(24歳)</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="countdown-section">
                <h2>🚀 出発まであと...</h2>
                <div class="countdown-timer" id="countdownTimer">
                    <div class="countdown-unit">
                        <span class="countdown-number" id="days">-</span>
                        <span class="countdown-label">日</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="countdown-unit">
                        <span class="countdown-number" id="hours">-</span>
                        <span class="countdown-label">時間</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="countdown-unit">
                        <span class="countdown-number" id="minutes">-</span>
                        <span class="countdown-label">分</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="countdown-unit">
                        <span class="countdown-number" id="seconds">-</span>
                        <span class="countdown-label">秒</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="progress-bar">
                <div class="progress-fill" id="progressBar"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="progress-text" id="progressText">冒険の準備: 0% 完了</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Excitement Meter -->
        <div class="excitement-meter">
            <h2>🎊 家族のワクワクメーター 🎊</h2>
            <div class="excitement-bar">
                <div class="excitement-fill" id="excitementFill"></div>
            </div>
            <p id="excitementText">みんなの気持ち: ワクワク開始！ 0% 🌱</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Family Mission -->
        <div class="family-mission">
            <h3 class="mission-title">🎯 今回の家族ミッション</h3>
            <ul class="mission-list">
                <li>朝市で新鮮な食材をゲットせよ！</li>
                <li>飛騨牛の美味しいハンバーガーを作ろう！</li>
                <li>朴葉味噌の秘密を解き明かせ！</li>
                <li>焚き火とサウナで大人のリラックスタイム</li>
                <li>古川の美しい風景をInstagramに！</li>
                <li>家族3人で地酒を楽しもう🍶</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Fun Features -->
        <div class="fun-features">
            <div class="feature-card" onclick="playSound()">
                <span class="feature-icon">🎵</span>
                <h3>家族プレイリスト</h3>
                <p>みんなで選んだ旅行BGM</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card" onclick="showRandomTip()">
                <span class="feature-icon">💡</span>
                <h3>旅行のコツ</h3>
                <p>より楽しむためのヒント集</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card" onclick="takeFamilyPhoto()">
                <span class="feature-icon">📸</span>
                <h3>思い出写真</h3>
                <p>家族3人の素敵な瞬間を記録</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Day 1 -->
        <div class="day-section">
            <div class="day-header">
                <div class="day-number">1</div>
                <div class="day-title">
                    <h2>9月27日（土）🌅</h2>
                    <div class="day-subtitle">食材調達大作戦 → 高山散策 → WAT RESORT BBQ祭り！</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline">
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="time-badge">🚗 05:30</div>
                    <div class="activity-title">富山市婦中町西本郷 大冒険スタート！</div>
                    <div class="activity-description">早起きして朝市の新鮮食材をゲットしよう！家族3人でのんびりドライブ♪</div>
                    <ul class="checklist">
                        <li><input type="checkbox" id="departure" onchange="updateProgress(); checkCompleted(this);"><span>🚗 車の点検完了（パパの腕の見せ所）</span></li>
                        <li><input type="checkbox" id="fuel" onchange="updateProgress(); checkCompleted(this);"><span>⛽ ガソリン満タン確認</span></li>
                        <li><input type="checkbox" id="cooler" onchange="updateProgress(); checkCompleted(this);"><span>🧊 クーラーボックス準備OK</span></li>
                        <li><input type="checkbox" id="coffee" onchange="updateProgress(); checkCompleted(this);"><span>☕ 車内用コーヒー準備（みんなで眠気覚まし）</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="time-badge">🌅 07:00</div>
                    <div class="activity-title">飛騨高山宮川朝市 - 食材ハンティング大作戦！</div>
                    <div class="activity-description">新鮮野菜と朴葉味噌の材料をゲット！息子さんも食材選びに参加</div>
                    
                    <div class="shopping-list">
